# ProductHeader

The IDS Product Header displays important actions the user can perform in the application.

This component is currently experimental and its API is subject to change.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/product-header
```

```tsx
import { ProductHeader } from '@ids-ts/product-header';
```

## Props API

<details>
<summary>Full TypeScript Interface</summary>

```typescript
export type ProductHeaderProps = ThemeableElement<'header'>;
```

</details>

